1. Download MongoDB Sample dataset from
https://github.com/srimarrivada/mongodb-sample-dataset

2. Download MongoDB Command Line Database Tools from 
https://www.mongodb.com/try/download/database-tools

3. Go to location where MongoDB tools are downloaded

4. Start importing sample dataset into MongoDB local instance using mongoimport utility

mongoimport.exe --host localhost --port 27017 --db sample_analytics --collection listingsAndReviews --file E:\Software\MongoDB\mongodb-sample-dataset-main\sample_analytics\listingsAndReviews.json

or

mongoimport.exe --db sample_airbnb --collection listingsAndReviews --file E:\Software\MongoDB\mongodb-sample-dataset-main\sample_analytics\listingsAndReviews.json

mongoimport.exe --db sample_analytics --collection accounts --file E:\Software\MongoDB\mongodb-sample-dataset-main\sample_analytics\accounts.json
